When I was doing LGUK I'd get tells all the time to come do a rez. The same groups every 15 mins asking for rezzes. Mind you have a chanter with me 90% of the time so I'm cracked all the time and have the mana to pull frenzied guy do a rez heal the MT and heal the rezzie when he zones in. So downtime is not much in the situation. most of the time I'm asked to go find the corpse drag it to the zone and rez them. It's down time from my group. If I have time to play 1 to 3 hours a night then taking the 15 to 20 mins to take care of this person rez is a hugh chunk of my time to play my game. So making some pp for taking up my time I have to play EQ is not asking too much.<br>
<br>
I do take donations if offered. I do. do I expect one to be offered. Yes! unless it for the guild my group or a friend. I just saved you time, and a level possibly. If you are below level 25 and want a rez Pay for it! The time to takes for you to find the rez get the cleric there wait for the rez effect to wear off. You could of ran back gotten your corpse and gotten most of the EXP back. The rez you are getting is an Extra that you don't need.<br>
